<li><a href="http://www.digitalpreservation.gov/formats/fdd/fdd000016.shtml" class="external text" title="http://www.digitalpreservation.gov/formats/fdd/fdd000016.shtml" rel="nofollow">Information about PCM</a>: A description of PCM with links to information about subtypes of this format (for example <a href="/wiki/Linear_Pulse_Code_Modulation" title="Linear Pulse Code Modulation" class="mw-redirect">Linear Pulse Code Modulation</a>), and references to their specifications.</li>
</ul>


